  '<p><code>b.cryptoField</code> is the middleware <code>b.db</code> uses internally to seal and unseal columns. Operators rarely call it directly, but it\'s reachable when a feature stores ciphertext outside the DB and wants the same envelope shape. Full envelope details live at <a href="/crypto-vault#envelope">Crypto &amp; Vault → envelope</a>.</p>',
